            <lg xml:id="TK674">
<l>viṉaipakai yeṉṟiraṇṭi ṉecca niṉaiyuṅkāṟ </l>
<l>ṟīyeccam pōlat teṟum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>When duly considered, the incomplete execution of an undertaking and hostility will grow and destroy one like the (unextinguished) remnant of a fire</l>
            </lg>
